The Knights of Ardougne are knights found in the West Ardougne.

After the events of Plague's End, they replace all the mourners within West Ardougne and the Mourner Headquarters. These Knights have the different stats comparing to the mourners they replace, and those replacing unattackable mourners can likewise not be attacked. The mourners on the surface of West Ardougne have no drops besides bones, but those in the Mourner Headquarters have the same drops as the mourners there do, with the exception of the mourner outfit, which can instead be obtained from a chest inside what was formerly the Head Mourner's office. Oddly, those inside the office count for Elf slayer assignments.
